STEPS TO INSTALL
!!! WONT WORK WITHOUT !!!

REQUIRES BUN SH:
    install at: https://bun.sh/



1. build main.ts:
    `bun build ./src/main/main.ts --target node --outfile ./src/main/main.js`

2. Build rest of typescript:
    `bun build.ts`

3. Build SCSS ( css ):
    index: `bun sass ./src/index/style.scss ./src/index/style.css`
    settings: `bun sass ./src/settings/settings.scss ./src/settings/settings.css `

App is build

To start:
    Live: `bun dev`
    Static: `bun start`

To build app to executable:
    `bunx electron-builder'